<h3 id="Gentoo_40ebuild_41_based_distributions">  Gentoo (ebuild) based distributions </h3>
<p></p>

<div class="twistyPlugin foswikiMakeVisible"><span id="twistyIdSystemSystemRequirements9793show" style="display:none" class="twistyTrigger foswikiUnvisited twistyInited"><a class="" href="#"><span class="foswikiLinkLabel foswikiUnvisited">Show Gentoo details</span></a></span><span id="twistyIdSystemSystemRequirements9793hide" style="display:none" class="twistyTrigger foswikiUnvisited twistyInited"><a class="" href="#"><span class="foswikiLinkLabel foswikiUnvisited">Hide Gentoo details</span></a></span></div><div class="twistyPlugin"><div id="twistyIdSystemSystemRequirements9793toggle" style="" class="twistyContent twistyInited">
<p></p>

<h4 id="Minimum_requirements_AN2">  Minimum requirements </h4>
<p></p>

Install <code>www-servers/apache</code>, <code>dev-vcs/rcs</code>, and <code>dev-lang/perl</code>
<p></p>

