<h5 id="To_install_the_above_packages_on_Gentoo">  To install the above packages on Gentoo </h5>
<p></p>

<blockquote>
<code>emerge</code> <code>dev-perl/Algorithm-Diff</code> <code>perl-Archive-Tar</code> <code>dev-perl/Authen-SASL</code> <code>dev-perl/CGI</code> <code>dev-perl/CGI-Session</code> <code>dev-perl/Crypt-PasswdMD5</code>  <code>dev-perl/Email-MIME</code> <code>dev-perl/Error</code>  <code>dev-perl/File-Copy-Recursive</code> <code>dev-perl/HTML-Parser</code> <code>dev-perl/HTML-Tree</code>  <code>dev-perl/IO-Socket-SSL</code> <code>dev-perl/JSON</code>  <code>dev-perl/Locale-Maketext-Lexicon</code> <code>dev-perl/Locale-Msgfmt</code> <code>dev-perl/libwww-perl</code> <code>dev-perl/URI</code>
</blockquote>
<p></p>

<h4 id="Optional_dependencies_AN2">  Optional dependencies </h4>
<p class='p'>Install as needed.</p>

<table class="foswikiTable" id="tableSystemRequirements7" rules="none">
	<thead>
		<tr class="foswikiTableOdd foswikiTableRowdataBgSorted0 foswikiTableRowdataBg0">
			<th class="foswikiTableCol0 foswikiFirstCol"> Perl Module </th>
