			<td class="foswikiTableCol0 foswikiFirstCol"> URI </td>
			<td class="foswikiTableCol1"> <code>p5-URI</code> </td>
			<td class="foswikiTableCol2 foswikiLastCol"> &nbsp; </td>
		</tr>
		<tr class="foswikiTableOdd foswikiTableRowdataBgSorted1 foswikiTableRowdataBg1">
			<td class="foswikiTableCol0 foswikiFirstCol foswikiLast"> version </td>
			<td class="foswikiTableCol1 foswikiLast"> <code>p5-version</code> </td>
			<td class="foswikiTableCol2 foswikiLastCol foswikiLast"> Must be version 0.77 or newer, included with perl 5.10.1 and newer. </td>
		</tr>
	</tbody></table>
<p></p>

<h5 id="To_install_the_above_packages_on_FreeBSD">  To install the above packages on FreeBSD </h5>
<p></p>

<blockquote>
<code>pkg install</code> <code>p5-Algorithm-Diff</code> <code>p5-Archive-Tar</code> <code>p5-Authen-SASL</code> <code>p5-CGI</code> <code>p5-CGI-Session</code> <code>p5-Crypt-PasswdMD5</code> <code>p5-Digest-SHA</code> <code>p5-Email-MIME</code> <code>p5-Encode</code> <code>p5-Error</code> <code>p5-File-Copy-Recursive</code> <code>p5-HTML-Parser</code> <code>p5-HTML-Tree</code> <code>p5-IO-Socket-IP</code> <code>p5-IO-Socket-SSL</code> <code>p5-JSON</code> <code>p5-Locale-Maketext</code> <code>p5-Locale-Maketext-Lexicon</code> <code>p5-Locale-Msgfmt</code> <code>p5-libwww</code> <code>p5-URI</code> <code>p5-version</code>
</blockquote>
<p></p>

After expanding the Foswiki archive, change the ownership of the files: <ul>
<li> <code>chown -R www:wwwadmin /var/www/path-to-foswiki</code>
</li></ul> 
<p></p>

